 Frame of Suit-Whether earlier giving up a cause of action by deletion from the plaint and later on again re for inclusion of the same cause is barred by the principle of Order II of Rule 2 C.P.C.
 Doctrine of constructive Res-judicata-When it applies- Whether deletion of a cause of action from the plaint and again a request for inclusion would amount to a bar of Res- judicata.
 Delhi Rent Control Act, Section 25B-Whether violative of Art. 14 of the Constitution.
 
